      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以WAITING_FILE状态是由PaymentGateway触发的。那如果没有文件的情况呢？是直接走另一条分支吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
