      "utterance": "对，无文件的情况由FinTech_TransactionQueue直接连到SENDING状态。然后SENDING之后统一走到REGISTERED，表示在SEND系统里创建了实体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
