      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "COMPLETE之后还有一个关键步骤：要变成ACCEPTED状态，这个ACCEPTED状态也适用于SEND系统。最后ACCEPTED要回到FinTech_TransactionQueue形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
