      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，ACCEPTED是COMPLETE的下一个状态，然后终点指向TransactionQueue。整个图的标题就用\"Stati send_notification\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
