      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，标题就用意大利语的\"Stati send_notification\"。另外各条转移线我标注一下业务含义，比如PaymentGateway到WAITING_FILE是\"Presenza di file da caricare\"，TransactionQueue到SENDING是\"No file\"。",
